lead_paragraph: Hoffenheim remained unbeaten and visitors Hamburg SV were still without a win after 11 games of the Bundesliga season following a pulsating 2-2 draw on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Hoffenheim Stay Unbeaten and Hamburg Winless After Draw
